{"tid":685764,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"RubberBand新歌 —— 逆流之歌 (電影《逆流大叔》主題曲)","createTime":"2018-05-31T16:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T07:57:20.000Z","uid":4260,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"17d671fec929b4f7d0fe244e0c12a83391ea9e41","tid":685764,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kfs.io/album/hk/35334349,0v1/fit/500x500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kfs.io%2Falbum%2Fhk%2F35334349%2C0v1%2Ffit%2F500x500.jpg&h=d754d7ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《逆流大叔》導演 陳詠燊：<br />\n<br />\n在討論《逆流大叔》需要一首怎樣的主題曲之時，我說：「我不想要一首假大空的勵志歌。」假大空的意思是，不停地標榜「有夢想就一定得」、「做就一定會成功」⋯<br />\n因為，太假了。活了這麼多年，你與我都知道，這根本不是人生的真相。<br />\n真相是甚麼？當然我都說不出來，但我相信失敗與成功之間，還有一個層次，就是做回你自己。做自己最後會如何？不知道，但至少跟著自己的心走，你才有能力找到真正屬於自己的出口。<br />\n<br />\n第一次聽到《逆流之歌》的時候，我眼眶都濕了。因為我最想說的話，RubberBand都用音樂替我傳達了出來。<br />\n<br />\n坐上龍舟，你只有一件事可以做，就是認清自己的鼓聲，破浪前行。<br />\n<br />\n人生，也一樣。<br />\n<br />\n作詞：RubberBand    作曲：RubberBand<br />\n編曲：RubberBand    監製：RubberBand<br />\n<br />\nKKBOX: <a href=\"https://kkbox.fm/jSMMiE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkkbox.fm%2FjSMMiE&d=22rjw7MZQzEBVDU82dJsoDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=251470aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kkbox.fm/jSMMiE</a><br />\nMOOV: <a href=\"https://s.moov.hk/r?s=VgZKQe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.moov.hk%2Fr%3Fs%3DVgZKQe&d=22rjw7MZQzEBVDU82dJsoDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b24f932d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.moov.hk/r?s=VgZKQe</a><br />\nJOOX: <a href=\"http://www.joox.com/hk/zh_hk/album/4058686\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.joox.com%2Fhk%2Fzh_hk%2Falbum%2F4058686&d=22rjw7MZQzEBVDU82dJsoDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=51dded76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.joox.com/hk/zh_hk/album/4058686</a><br />\nSpotify: <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/album/42fHshck5EhiCEV9QO4Vol?si=Hc8KaxnAQ2eJdpszPmNmJg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Falbum%2F42fHshck5EhiCEV9QO4Vol%3Fsi%3DHc8KaxnAQ2eJdpszPmNmJg&d=22rjw7MZQzEBVDU82dJsoDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=fe869e18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://open.spotify.com/album/42fHshck5EhiCEV9QO4Vol?si=Hc8KaxnAQ2eJdpszPmNmJg</a><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，呢齣電影係講述幾個從事寛頻維修既員工，為左保住佢地既飯碗，不惜加入公司新成立既龍舟隊，從而搵返人生出口既故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c8f9ee9b2a960db3e6c143f71900e5b3695bff","tid":685764,"uid":4260,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:18:05.000Z","msg":"黎緊「H」大碟《Hours》率先曝光兩首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《脫軌時刻 》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PTgV7Z_hrsM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPTgV7Z_hrsM&d=22rjw7MZQzEBVDU82dJsoDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5455bc18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PTgV7Z_hrsM</a><br />\n<br />\n《城市當代配樂團》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ENl3CoeCk_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DENl3CoeCk_Y&d=22rjw7MZQzEBVDU82dJsoDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=727ad583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ENl3CoeCk_Y</a>"},{"pid":"a6e036887a4401ef7c7185c54086035eb6715d6b","tid":685764,"uid":4260,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:20:00.000Z","msg":"翻多少山丘方發覺<br />\n躲不開這生存肉搏<br />\n啃多少海水至清楚<br />\n怎給這一生反撲<br />\n<br />\n衝出這裏 憑我身軀<br />\n<br />\n拼了所有 斷氣方休<br />\n靠我呼吸捲起整個宇宙<br />\n縱會失勢 碰上關口<br />\n聽到心裡鼓聲穿透<br />\n<br />\n航向那出口<br />\n<br />\n湍急的一生飛快掠過<br />\n追趕不到一場幻覺<br />\n分岔口之中在奔波<br />\n怎把握真的知覺<br />\n<br />\n衝出這裏 憑我身軀<br />\n<br />\n拼了所有 斷氣方休<br />\n靠我呼吸捲起整個宇宙<br />\n縱會失勢 碰上關口<br />\n聽到心裡鼓聲穿透<br />\n<br />\n我未有顫抖<br />\n<br />\n歲月將一切淘空<br />\n但我守好那片夢<br />\n哪懼髮白再滿身疼痛<br />\n<br />\n拼了所有 斷氣方休<br />\n靠我呼吸捲起整個宇宙<br />\n縱會失勢 碰上關口<br />\n聽到心中鼓聲穿過悲憂<br />\n<br />\n拼了所有 不息不休<br />\n靠我呼吸捲起整個宇宙<br />\n試過失勢 誰人沒有<br />\n聽到心中鼓聲穿透<br />\n航向那出口"},{"pid":"d4a863bc97f8993b9c230ad6e577455450ed51ca","tid":685764,"uid":72972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 6號把聲好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fbcf7e473f4a3e828627bde9992dc9d66488e7","tid":685764,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:39:33.000Z","msg":"歌名無創意 概念抄沙燕之歌"},{"pid":"753b3840f3ba9481447ba56f7dc3fa92116f128f","tid":685764,"uid":66856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"終於有新歌聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270199aa1a3179df58edccee0f60a8dd08cfd4af","tid":685764,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"753b3840f3ba9481447ba56f7dc3fa92116f128f","tid":685764,"uid":66856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"終於有新歌聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:29:10.000Z","msg":"9月26號演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383085e0a3f2942100e1eb7dfb371099ffcfd64a","tid":685764,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4a863bc97f8993b9c230ad6e577455450ed51ca","tid":685764,"uid":72972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 6號把聲好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好快又有新歌聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2b7ab7cabba0be08fe2959e51956bdbc77a157","tid":685764,"uid":4260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:19:00.000Z","msg":"RubberBand<br />\nYesterday at 14:12 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n啲人成日問點解我哋今年好似好靜成日見我哋唔到咁，其實唔通我哋不停匿埋咗做嘢又話你知咩？<br />\n除咗密密做碟錄音同做早兩日你哋睇得好開心嗰條片首廣告歌之外，其實今年仲做咗一個新嘗試。<br />\n話說一間好勇敢嘅電影公司搵咗個新導演 陳詠燊 Sunnyhahaha 拍咗套戲，咁都未算最勁，最勁係佢哋好似嫌自己仲未夠勇咁，轉個頭仲搵咗我哋四個做第一次嘅電影配樂。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋咁勇我哋唯有玩埋一份啦，我哋走咗去挑戰人哋嘅電影宣傳schedule，搶先派咗首主題曲出街先！<br />\n天氣咁熱，唔聽呢啲熱血嘢聽咩吖？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71be62087509e897bffde0ed1b68e113d6b8ee85","tid":685764,"uid":4260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T04:56:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=l437aFu-29g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl437aFu-29g&d=22rjw7MZQzEBVDU82dJsoDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=12a3bd20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=l437aFu-29g</a><br />\nMv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40306b4d0fb0e3fb07af010b0ab2f53eef24d41","tid":685764,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad2b7ab7cabba0be08fe2959e51956bdbc77a157","tid":685764,"uid":4260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:19:00.000Z","msg":"RubberBand<br />\nYesterday at 14:12 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n啲人成日問點解我哋今年好似好靜成日見我哋唔到咁，其實唔通我哋不停匿埋咗做嘢又話你知咩？<br />\n除咗密密做碟錄音同做早兩日你哋睇得好開心嗰條片首廣告歌之外，其實今年仲做咗一個新嘗試。<br />\n話說一間好勇敢嘅電影公司搵咗個新導演 陳詠燊 Sunnyhahaha 拍咗套戲，咁都未算最勁，最勁係佢哋好似嫌自己仲未夠勇咁，轉個頭仲搵咗我哋四個做第一次嘅電影配樂。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋咁勇我哋唯有玩埋一份啦，我哋走咗去挑戰人哋嘅電影宣傳schedule，搶先派咗首主題曲出街先！<br />\n天氣咁熱，唔聽呢啲熱血嘢聽咩吖？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 